=\"fill\" sizes=\"50vw\" srcset=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AllisonLewis-tdf-homes19.jpg\u0026amp;w=384\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 384w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AllisonLewis-tdf-homes19.jpg\u0026amp;w=768\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 768w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AllisonLewis-tdf-homes19.jpg\u0026amp;w=1440\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1440w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AllisonLewis-tdf-homes19.jpg\u0026amp;w=1920\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1920w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AllisonLewis-tdf-homes19.jpg\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 2560w\" src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/AllisonLewis-tdf-homes19.jpg\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBedside Tables\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you do keep the bed relatively simple, why not select something a bit more playful for the bedside table?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/kartell-componibili-bio-3-round-storage-unit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eKartell Componibili Bio 3 Round Storage Unit\u003c/a\u003e from Space Furniture has a funky silhouette and sliding doors where your little one can keep their favourite objects, or perhaps make a statement with the bold \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/chub-table\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eChub Table\u003c/a\u003e from local brand Fearon.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor something slightly more 