 Cult is designed especially for children between 3 and 12 years old.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"NaN\" height=\"NaN\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"50vw\" srcset=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-7.webp\u0026amp;w=384\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 384w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-7.webp\u0026amp;w=768\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 768w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-7.webp\u0026amp;w=1440\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1440w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-7.webp\u0026amp;w=1920\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1920w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-7.webp\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 2560w\" src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-7.webp\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"NaN\" height=\"NaN\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"50vw\" srcset=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-16.webp\u0026amp;w=384\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 384w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-16.webp\u0026amp;w=768\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 768w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-16.webp\u0026amp;w=1440\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1440w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-16.webp\u0026amp;w=1920\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 1920w, https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-16.webp\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp 2560w\" src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-16.webp\u0026amp;w=2560\u0026amp;q=75\u0026amp;output=webp\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLighting\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA little lamp is a good way to bring a pop of colour to a kid’s room. We love Fenton \u0026amp; Fenton’s \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/cindy-table-lamp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eCindy Table Lamp\u003c/a\u003e with its candy pink stripes, while the \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/arum-portable-lamp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eArum Portable Lamp\u003c/a\u003e from Trit House is a good portable option without cords — allowing you to use it as a reading lamp at night and easily move it out of reach afterwards.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAnd you can’t go past the \u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory/product/george-nelson-saucer-bubble-pendant\"\u003eGeorge Nelson Saucer Bubble Pendant\u003c/a\u003e from Lights Lights Lights. Investing in an elegant pendant light will instantly elevate the space, making sure it’s stylish for young kids all the way up to teenage children, and beyond!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb data-stringify-type=\"bold\"\u003e\u003ci data-stringify-type=\"italic\"\u003eWant to see more? Visit \u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cb data-stringify-type=\"bold\"\u003e\u003ci data-stringify-type=\"italic\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thedesignfiles.wpenginepowered.com/directory\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-stringify-link=\"/directory\" data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\"